cd                         ✅ sahi folder mein jao
git init                   ✅ Git ko bolo "is folder ko track karo"
git remote add origin URL  ✅ GitHub repo se connect karo
git add .                  ✅ saari files tayyar karo (envelope mein daalo)
git commit -m "message"    ✅ snapshot lo
git push -u origin main    ✅ GitHub par upload karo


Example usage

1st : cd "D:\Python\Mega PROJECT 1. JARVIS"  ---> folder ki location  
2nd: git init
3rd: git remote add origin "https://github.com/usmandevcs/Jarvis-ai-assistant.git"  --->  URL ha Github repo ka 
4th: git add .
5th: git commit -m "JARVIS AI Assistant - initial commit" ---> message aur screenshot lelo 
6th: git push -u origin main

7th: code .gitignore  ---> is se aik file open hoti jo cheezy hum nhi upload karna chahty wo is me add kardy gy jis se wo ignore jaye gi
